descriptionap back to ToC or Annotation Property ToC

IRI: http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/description

has sub-properties
Abstractap, Descriptionap, Table Of Contentsap
CEVO (i.e., a comprehensive event ontology) is an ontology for enhancing your cognitive annotations of your data. It was built upon Levin's conceptual hierarchy of English verbs. This conceptual hierarchy categorizes verbs with the shared meaning or behavior. CEVO defines a hierarchy of events. Each event has a couple of associated verbs which manifest that event.
